# Copy to .env.local and fill in. Never commit real keys.

# --- SoSoValue OpenAPI (required for the ETF-flow de-risk signal) ---
# Without this, vaults still show live SoDEX funding, but the institutional-flow signal that
# drives de-risk stays in its "connect key" state.
# Get a key: register at sosovalue.com, then request API access in the API docs. For the
# Buildathon, use the access form to raise limits.
SOSOVALUE_API_KEY=
# Optional overrides:
# SOSOVALUE_API_BASE=https://openapi.sosovalue.com/openapi/v1
# SOSOVALUE_RATE_LIMIT_PER_MIN=20

# --- SoDEX (public market data needs no key; testnet by default) ---
# SODEX_NETWORK=testnet
# SODEX_API_BASE=https://testnet-gw.sodex.dev

# --- AI narration (optional; grounded explanations of vault state) ---
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# --- Funding/flow history (the track-record moat) ---
# Default store writes to the OS temp dir (ephemeral on serverless). Set a persistent path,
# or swap the HistoryStore for a database, for durable history.
# HISTORY_FILE=
# Protects the /api/cron/snapshot endpoint; Vercel Cron sends it as a Bearer token.
# CRON_SECRET=
